    "This has encouraged companies to integrate ESG metrics into integrated reports, linking sustainability efforts to financial outcomes.",
    "However, the expansion of ESG reporting has also highlighted fragmentation in methodologies, divergence in ratings, and inconsistencies in assurance practices [4].Figure 1 illustrates global adoption rates of ESG reporting across key regions and correlates them with emerging AI adoption trends in ESG data processing and reporting.",
